tool_description: The API is scraping the Wikipedia pages for dogs in order to collect data
name: Dog breeds
title: Dog breeds

api_list.name: Group breed data by property
api_list.description:
This endpoint will group the available data by the given property and the property value. The property can be any property of the JSON response object including the properties of the meta object. 

The API will return all dog breeds that are matching the property value that is given.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://dog-breeds2.p.rapidapi.com/dog_breeds/group/breed_status/extinct"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "dog-breeds2.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
